            "user_id": "U_CONTENT_STRAT",
            "text": "Hi team - updated Q1 repurposing criteria from the strategy session. Please apply ALL of the following rules for this sprint:\n1. Only repurpose posts published within the last 6 months (on or after 2025-07-27). Older content is out of scope for Q1 automated repurposing regardless of traffic.\n2. Do NOT add posts where the target format is already listed in the repurposed_formats column. If a format is already adapted, skip it.\n3. Content tagged Evergreen Gold in the notes column must go through editorial review. Do NOT add Evergreen Gold posts to the automated queue - they are handled separately.\n4. Each queue entry MUST include a per-item tracking code in the format REPR-<content_id>-Q1 (e.g., REPR-C001-Q1 for content row 1, REPR-C007-Q1 for row 7). This is in addition to the batch code.\nThis message supersedes any previous general criteria from content-director@. CEO-level overrides on specific posts still apply.",
